nuclear tests in May and immediately imposed sanctions on the two
countries.
</P>
<P>
It at the same time called on India and Pakistan to refrain
from further testing as it could fuel a regional arms race or even
spark conflict.
</P>
<P>
Talbott last week also told journalists that the United States
was trying to use the diplomatic way to resolve the issue.
</P>
<P>
