<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, July 7 (Xinhua) -- In the first half of the year,
customs officers in Gongbei in China's Guangdong Province dealt
with 523 cases of smuggling, involving 146 million yuan worth of
smuggled goods.
</P>
<P>
