<HEADLINE> Potential Gold Jewelry Market In China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Demand for gold jewelry in China is
still strong and has great potential, according to Liu Shengyu, of
China Jewelry Import and Export Company, who spoke at a
publication ceremony today for a Chinese journal on the world's
