<TEXT>

<P>
PARIS, July 7 (Xinhua) -- French team doctor warned his team not
to play another extra-time in the semi-final match against Croatia
on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
"If they play extra-time again, it will be difficult for them
physically," said team doctor Jean-Marcel Ferret, "I'm sure they can
be 100 percent for 90 minutes. But if they have to play for longer
than that they might tire."
</P>
