impact of the economic crisis which has spread through the region.
</P>
<P>
Surin will also discuss bilateral issues with Foreign Minister
Ali Alatas.
</P>
<P>
Surin will start his trip to Australia on Thursday and return
to Bangkok next Wednesday.
</P>
