Sukhumbhand Paribatra will on Wednesday travel to Bangladesh where
he will discuss the progress of BIMSTEC or
Bangladesh-India-Myanmar-Sri Lanka-Thailand Economic Cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Sukhumbhand will also co-sign an extradition treaty with
Bangladesh. 
